BUA Cement is to be listed on the Nigerian Stock Exchange (NSE) today, Thursday. BUA Cement Plc is listing after the just-concluded merger between Cement Company of Northern Nigeria (CCNN) and Obu Cement. The management of BUA Cement Plc are already on the (NSE) as part of activities for the listing. The listing of BUA Cement broadens the number of stocks listed on the building materials/construction subsector of the Exchange. The company will be honoured with a closing gong ceremony by 2:30pm in Lagos. BUA Cement is listing its stock when the bullish run continues on the Exchange driven by investorsâ€™ interest in value counters and positioning ahead of dividend yield amid full year financials coming soon.